  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want my options to be more obvious to me on the home/chat screen so that I can start chats more easily.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: In #7534, we're separating DApps into their own tab and renaming the `Home` tab to `Chat`. \r\n\r\nThe new `Chat` screen will be redesigned to have the `+` icon in the bottom center (rather than top right), with fewer options.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n`+` button from current Home screen is relocated to bottom center. Bottom sheet is used to give users the additional chat options, `Start new chat`, `Start group chat`, etc.\r\n\r\nThere are no longer options relating to DApps. \r\n\r\n[DESIGNS](https://www.figma.com/file/deXIBZm6fU1CCL0voYbfTujz/Navigation?node-id=1%3A2)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe current Home screen forces users to search for browser items from hard-to-notice `+` icon in upper right corner.",
